{
  "stem": "2713.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is the life in this camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Germans were always asking for more people, because people were dying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- he needed people for-- for the things that we were doing for the ammunition factories.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were women with us, as well, working in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're mainly the ones who were yellow more than the men, because they had the job, where they were working on those things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In same camp, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In different barracks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the same camp, different barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING] And as the German was asking for the-- for more people, every month, one day they told him, you'd better look after your people, because, if you won't look after your people, you-- you know where you finish up?",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You go to the front.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he could see that he-- he's risking his life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So things were starting to get better in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Instead of 18 people a bread, there were 8 people for a bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The soup was already a soup.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could really call it, that you had a soup.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what they did, which was the main thing for us-- you know all those people that went to the gas chambers in Belzec or Treblinka?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Their clothes came to our camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we didn't know, but one-- it happened so that one boy undid something, and he found money and those things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we realized that there could be money in those things that we are getting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember, like today, I teared off a pair of shoes and gold and Russian peoples-- Russian-- Rubles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--money came from the-- from the boots.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You undid a belt, and there were-- there was money or gold or something in whatever you took.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
